schools.name: H T Faulk Early Childhood School

data.description: Close to Wheeler and an Elementary school, and "right around the corner" from the High School, this sought-after neighborhood doesn't often have a 4-bedroom For Sale, until now. Less than 20 years old, this 3-sides brick + Hardie home offers a great layout with split Primary Suite and large open kitchen/dining areas. The kitchen features a 2-tier counter with breakfast bar, upgraded 2-section oven, 9 foot ceilings, and a dining area easily big enough for a 6-top. The Primary Suite has a large bedroom area, long walk-in closet, walk-in shower, and garden tub. The other wing of the house contains 3 secondary bedrooms, with a large picture window in the front room for plenty of natural light (currently used as an office). ALL secondary bedrooms have good sized walk-in closets also. The laundry room boasts a storage nook with built-in shelves and above-the-appliance shelves. In the back, a concrete slab makes a great spot for the grill with lush grass in the yard. This one won't last long.
